 This spell shows you your surroundings.


Examples
 ls                      - shows you what is around your current position
 ls kitchen              - shows you what is in the directory my-house, assuming you are in my-house
 ls ../                  - shows you what is in the directory behind you
 ls ~/my-house/kitchen   - regardless of your current position, this will show you what is in your kitchen


Flags:
 -a                       - This shows all the files in your current directory, including the hidden files starting with .
                            This includes your current position . and the containing directory ..
Example
ls -a ../                 - Will show you everything in the directory behind you

